---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Horario semanal · CrossFit La Mola Terrassa"
  description="Horario semanal del box de CrossFit en Terrassa. Clases de lunes a domingo: WOD, halterofilia, hybrid, strength y más. Reserva por la app Aimharder."
  canonical="https://crossfitlamola.com/es/horari"
>
  <Nav currentPage="/es/horari" />

  <section class="page-hero" id="main">
    <div class="bg" style="background-image:url('/assets/community-5.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="crumb"><a href="/es">Inicio</a><span>/</span><span>Horario</span></div>
      <div class="kicker"><span>Semanal</span><span class="bar"></span><span>Reserva via Aimharder</span></div>
      <h1>El horario<br>de la <em class="serif">semana</em><span class="dot">.</span></h1>
      <p class="sub">Lunes a jueves de 7:00 a 21:30. Viernes de 7:00 a 20:30. Sábado y domingo de 9:30 a 11:30. Reserva por la app.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="status-strip">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span id="status"><span class="dot-live" id="statusDot"></span><span id="statusText">Abierto ahora</span></span>
      <span>Av. del Vallès 724C · Terrassa</span>
      <span>Lu-Ju 07:00-21:30 · Vi 07:00-20:30 · Sa-Do 09:30-11:30</span>
      <span style="margin-left:auto;"><a href="https://wa.me/34629066531" style="color:var(--accent-ink);">WhatsApp &rarr;</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="sec bone" style="padding-top:clamp(64px,8vw,120px);">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="num">01 —</span><span>Parrilla semanal</span></div>
      <div style="height:16px"></div>
      <div class="sec-head">
        <h2 class="h-xl reveal">Todas las<br>clases, <em class="serif">todas</em> las franjas<span class="dot">.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead reveal">Filtra por disciplina. Las clases con coach tienen capacidad limitada. Reserva con antelación especialmente en las franjas de mañana y tarde.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="toggle-row reveal">
        <label><input type="checkbox" id="showOpen"> Mostrar Open Gym y Open Exterior</label>
        <span style="opacity:.7;">Por defecto solo ves clases con coach</span>
      </div>

      <div class="filters reveal" id="filters">
        <button class="filter on" data-f="all">Todas <span class="count" id="c-all"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="wod">WOD <span class="count" id="c-wod"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="wl">Weightlifting <span class="count" id="c-wl"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="hy">Hybrid <span class="count" id="c-hy"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="bw">Bodyweight <span class="count" id="c-bw"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="st">Strength Club <span class="count" id="c-st"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="ab">Abs &amp; Cals <span class="count" id="c-ab"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="pr">The Program <span class="count" id="c-pr"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="rc">Running <span class="count" id="c-rc"></span></button>
        <button class="filter" data-f="etc">Entrena con coach <span class="count" id="c-etc"></span></button>
      </div>

      <div class="week reveal" id="week"></div>

      <div class="legend reveal">
        <span class="chip" style="--c:var(--bone-ink);">WOD</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:var(--accent-ink);">Weightlifting · Program</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:#3d5f3f;">Hybrid</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:#8c3f2f;">Strength</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:#5a4a2f;">Bodyweight</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:#7a4a3a;">Abs &amp; Cals</span>
        <span class="chip" style="--c:#3a5a7a;">Running</span>
      </div>

      <div class="meta-card reveal">
        <strong>Cómo reservar:</strong> Descarga la app <strong>Aimharder</strong> y regístrate con tu código. Puedes reservar <strong>desde 24h antes</strong>. Si has consumido tu cuota mensual, puedes hacer <strong>clases extra a 8€/clase</strong> o subir de tarifa.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-block">
    <div class="bg" style="background-image:url('/assets/class-program.webp')"></div>
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:var(--bone-3)"><span class="num" style="color:var(--accent-hi)">02 —</span><span>¿Primera vez?</span></div>
      <h2 class="h-hero reveal">Reserva<br>tu <em class="serif">primera</em><span class="dot">.</span></h2>
      <p class="reveal">Si es tu primer día, escríbenos antes y te preparamos una bienvenida adaptada a tu nivel.</p>
      <div class="actions reveal">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="/es/contacte">Reservar primera clase<span class="arr"></span></a>
        <a class="btn-ghost" href="/es/classes">Ver disciplinas</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />

